 Install the latest version of Rasbian os in the raspberry pi.
 Download the required cups driver for your printer from the cups official website on to the Raspberry pi.
 Install python in Raspberry.
 Write the python script and save the file. 
 Place the file in the boot folder of the raspberry pi so that the file runs whenever the pi is turned on.
 Create a website where we will upload the files that are to be printed, write the php script in the web page.
